# Deny collection-level permission (example)\ntfssecurity /g+ "Project Collection Valid Users" "user@example.com" ViewCollectionLevelInformation /deny /collection:https://tfs.example.com:8080/tfs/DefaultCollection\n\n# Grant project-level permission (example)\ntfssecurity /a+ "user@example.com" "Contributors" /collection:https://tfs.example.com:8080/tfs/DefaultCollection /project:YourProjectName